# Cloud is optional. Set BOTH vars to enable sign-in (and, later, sync + sharing).
# Leave them unset for the original local-only app — no auth UI, no network.
#
# These are PUBLIC, publishable values: the anon key is meant to ship in the
# browser bundle, and Row-Level Security (not key secrecy) is the security
# boundary. NEVER put the Supabase service_role key here.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (git-ignored) for local dev. In CI/Pages, set
# them as GitHub Actions repository *Variables* of the same name.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
